title: Filippo Inzaghi
summary: Filippo Inzaghi Ufficiale OMRI (Italian pronunciation: [fiˈlippo inˈtsaːɡi];[2] born 9 August 1973) is an Italian professional football manager and former player who played as a striker. He is the head coach of Serie B club Brescia Calcio. He was nicknamed "Superpippo" or "Alta tensione" by fans and commentators during his playing career.
